        "id": 5640
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-04-15T15:41:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Shouldn\u0027t be. EndFragmentProcessor() follows the call to ReleaseProgram() with End(), which sets the DSLWriter instance to null, so there\u0027s no way to end up with a null config and non-null DSLWriter instance (at least not without doing shady things using private APIs).",
      "parentUuid": "541ed4ad_ff7fd646",
      "range": {
